B.TQ=new A.cT("Use a single-page form instead of a multi-step wizard","User testing showed that the wizard created a false sense of progress and increased drop-off at step 3.","Task completion improved by 18% in the follow-up test round.",B.b9)
B.TG=new A.cT("Defer the notification preferences screen to post-onboarding","Stakeholders wanted it up front. We argued it added friction before users had context to make meaningful choices.","Shipped with compromise: one opt-in toggle at step one, full settings deferred. Both sides partially satisfied.",B.k5)
